sentence: In early trading on Tuesday, shares of 3M ( MMM ) topped the list of the day's best performing Dow Jones Industrial Average components, trading up 4.7%.
Year to date, 3M has lost about 4.4% of its value.
And the worst performing Dow component thus far on the day is Apple ( AAPL ), trading down 1.3%.
Apple is lower by about 6.7% looking at the year to date performance.
Two other components making moves today are UnitedHealth Group ( UNH ), trading down 1.2%, and Procter & Gamble ( PG ), trading up 2.8% on the day.
